title: N.F.L. Week 10 Predictions: Our Picks for Each Game
description: Josh Allen’s status puts the Bills’ matchup against the Vikings into disarray, the Seahawks look to extend their winning steak, and the 49ers are hoping for health out of their bye week.
dc:creator: David Hill
media:description: Will Josh Allen play on Sunday? The answer to that question is worth about 6 points in the spread.
